panama at least twice staying at the el panama hilton or the 
marriott records show 
the documents do not explain exactly what spencer did for 
panama spencer did not return two telephone calls and hecht said 
it is against his policy to discuss relations with clients 
but rep mike lowery dwash recalled a luncheon at the 
capitol hill club a republican haunt that he went to in january 
1986 at the invitation of the hecht staff 
the hecht people wanted to explore arranging better contacts 
between panamanian legislators and members of congress he said 
