the presence of soviet missiles in cuba during the 1962 missile 
crisis 
in spite of several allegations circulating in the west not 
once in the whole course of the conversation did kennedy raise the 
question of the presence of soviet missiles in cuba he wrote 
consequently i did not have to answer whether or not there 
were such weapons in cuba 
