missions to the middle east was to surround the gains of the 
islamic revolution in occupied palestine 
that suggested the kidnappers wanted secretary of state george 
p shultz to cancel a scheduled trip this week in which he is to 
visit jordan egypt and israel and may go to syria and saudi 
arabia 
