lawrenceville ga the gwinnett daily news will convert to 
morning publication in early may the newspaper announced in its 
feb 21 editions 
it currently publishes in the afternoon five days a week and in 
the morning on saturday and sunday 
executive editor jim osteen said moving to morning 
publication will allow us to produce a more expansive complete 
newspaper for our readers it will also allow our coverage of 
sports and the stock market report to be more timely 
the gwinnett daily news purchased in june by the new york 
times becomes the second suburban atlanta newspaper to switch from 
afternoon to morning publication the marietta daily journal 
announced similar plans earlier this year 
in the last 10 years more than 100 afternoon newspapers across 
the country have switched to morning publication 
