editors note born in a virginia hill town seka got 
interested in the porn business through her boyfriend who owned 
adult bookstores today shes a legend in the adultfilm industry 
as a performer and as an astute businesswoman 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
a porn queen who found her way to the other side 
of the camera is ascending toward the top in a 1 billionayear 
business where many women work but precious few call the shots 
shes a platinum blonde whose stage name is seka at 33 she has 
appeared in more than three dozen hardcore adult films over the 
past decade 
she is still legendary said paul fishbein publisher of 
adult video news magazine when todays generation delves into 
the adultfilm market for the first time she is still the one they 
want to see 
but the big reason for sekas financial success is that she sued 
her manager under federal corruption laws and gained control of her 
name her films and a business that turns annual profits in six 
figures 
dressed demurely in a sweater and slacks and tucked into the 
corner of a dark restaurant seka looks every bit the businesswoman 
she is as chief executive officer of the chicagobased pearl 
productions ltd which sells everything from lighters with her 
logo to panties 
nobody has ever taken care of me seka says 
matteroffactly running a bright pink fingernail through her 
closecropped platinum hair and as long as i look after 
business nobody ever will 
seka she will not disclose her given name was born in the 
virginia hill town of radford where the main industry was an 
arsenal that manufactures dynamite 
she married a factory worker before she finished high school 
but the marriage didnt last long 
all i knew was i wanted to be on my own i wanted to be 
independent she recalled i didnt want to wake up and have 
someone next to me saying fix me coffee and breakfast 
her introduction to the porn industry came during the mid1970s 
through a boyfriend who owned adult bookstores the more she became 
involved in the trade the more she became convinced i could do 
it better 
she worked her way back from the distributors she knew through 
the bookstore business to the moviemakers themselves went to 
california one bright day in 1977 answered an ad for a nude model 
and started working that afternoon 
seka was paid 200 for her first movie a 15minute 8mm film 
many of her early films she made more than two dozen between 
1977 and 1979 were only slightly more memorable although the pay 
scale improved considerably 
she was however just another 23yearold ingenue making adult 
films indistinguishable from dozens of other young women in the de 
rigeur black nylons and garter belts of the times then she met a 
makeup man with big plans it was 1980 and the homevideo market 
was just beginning to heat up 
he made her over bulked her up with weights and vitamins 
changed the way she dressed and managed her business in the 
bargain her new look debuted in 1981 in club magazine and the 
result was booming sales 
yet after what should have been a very profitable rise to the 
top of her profession seka had to hire an attorney simply to look 
at her own books one glimpse and she sued her manager for 
diverting income 
she worked sparingly over the next two years ultimately finding 
herself in 1984 with a handsome settlement and control of a 
potentially lucrative business now that the homevideo market was 
changing the rules of the adultfilm game 
no longer dependent on recovering most of the costs from 
theaters adult filmmaking became an almost riskfree venture 
a handful of pornographers had recognized the homevideo 
markets untapped potential ahead of the major movie studios and 
already were doing landoffice business 
a movie that could be made for as little as 150000 if shot on 
film or 20000 if shot directly onto videotape becomes a 
profitmaker after only moderate sales and rentals 
that meant an adult film had only to sell about 20000 
videocassettes an average wholesale cost of 25 per cassette to 
qualify as a megahit by comparison a major movie studio needs to 
sell 50000 units to approach the same status 
and seka needed only one look to realize that under the new 
economic reality age and overexposure were threatening her main 
asset her body 
so in 1984 she added a copyright attorney to gain control of her 
old material then a contract attorney to make certain she got top 
dollar for whatever new material she released 
she has made just two feature films since then only one has 
been released studied diction and elocution and devoted most of 
her time to mastering business skills computers flow charts 
marketing and the like 
her return to the adultfilm industry as an actress came in a 
big way with the 1986 film careful he may be watching the 
movie which cost about 230000 to make stars seka in a dual role 
as twins one evil one not 
she also conceived the story line developed the script and 
served as producer former porn star actor richard pacheco 
directed making the film something of a trailblazing effort from 
start to finish 
careful won the adult video news awards for best picture and 
best director capped off by sekas induction into the hall of 
fame but she says careful wont begin making money until its 
been on the market for about 2 years 
i can wait she said ive got some projects an exclusive 
magazine deal things i cant talk about in the wings ive even 
been offered the opportunity to be in a major motion picture but 
there were casting couches behind the screen 
at least what i do seka concluded is on the screen 
